{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Coordinates.heading","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/heading","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Geolocation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>GeolocationCoordinates</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/accuracy\"><code>accuracy</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitude\"><code>altitude</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/altitudeAccuracy\"><code>altitudeAccuracy</code></a></li><li><em><code>heading</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/latitude\"><code>latitude</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/longitude\"><code>longitude</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/speed\"><code>speed</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geolocation API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Coordinates.heading</strong></code> 是個唯讀的正複數用來代表裝置前進的方向。這個數值代表你偏離北方多少度，0度代表你向著正北方，照著順時針的方向遞增(90度代表正東方，270度代表正西方)。如果<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/speed\"><code>Coordinates.speed</code></a> 為0度，則此值為 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\">NaN</a></code>。如果這個裝置無法提供這個值則回傳 null。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"語法","title":"語法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>heading</var> = <var>coordinates</var>.heading\n</pre>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規格","id":"規格","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#heading-attribute","title":"Geolocation API"}],"query":"api.GeolocationCoordinates.heading"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器的相容性","id":"瀏覽器的相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GeolocationCoordinates.heading","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates/heading/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"請參考","title":"請參考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Using geolocation</a></li>\n <li>屬於 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>Coordinates</code></a> 介面。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"規格","id":"規格"},{"text":"瀏覽器的相容性","id":"瀏覽器的相容性"},{"text":"請參考","id":"請參考"}],"summary":"Coordinates.heading 是個唯讀的正複數用來代表裝置前進的方向。這個數值代表你偏離北方多少度，0度代表你向著正北方，照著順時針的方向遞增(90度代表正東方，270度代表正西方)。如果Coordinates.speed 為0度，則此值為 NaN。如果這個裝置無法提供這個值則回傳 null。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GeolocationCoordinates.heading","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GeolocationCoordinates.heading","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/geolocationcoordinates/heading","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/geolocationcoordinates/heading/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-